name: New Design File Setup Template - by @janustiu
description:
This Figma file contains some helpful templates with auto-layout for designers to set up new design projects.


Templates:

  • Project Cover
  • Project Plan
  • The Ask/ Problem Statement
  • Design Principles
  • Business Goals
  • Timeline
  • Task Status Bar


Follow @janustiu on Instagram for more UX design tips and resources.
